{"tid":911664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可憐小隻馬遭癡漢戴套性侵　還被怨會傳病","createTime":"2018-11-22T05:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T19:01:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"918134d0001ddc6db608d23ad5d332a57e6ca3a5","tid":911664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州一隻小隻馬「傑克G」(Jackie G)，慘遭21歲癡漢薩爾多(Nicholas Sardo)多次性侵，薩爾多還嫌牠會傳染疾病，因此都會戴保險套做愛。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這隻迷你馬是薩爾多一名親戚所養，但薩爾多卻多次對牠性侵，曾有女子直擊薩爾多在家族成員的牧場裡，性侵傑克G。另外還有一名女子也目擊過薩爾多的猥褻行為，並向女子承認性侵犯行。目前薩爾多已被警方逮捕，他承認性侵傑克G，一周至少性侵4次，而他擔心會被傑克G傳染病，因此都會帶套做愛。<br />\n目前薩爾多被控4項虐待動物以及與動物性交等罪名，但警方未公布小隻馬的傷勢。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_ff707b2486b156149fefd72929a5117e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_ff707b2486b156149fefd72929a5117e.jpg&h=2d58a6cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_63c2bb9936ce3478e9bdcd4c8cc7f7fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_63c2bb9936ce3478e9bdcd4c8cc7f7fe.jpg&h=8094a9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181122/1470933/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181122%2F1470933%2F&d=dfeeB01biWcpSatpjJUPMzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e916665c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181122%2F1470933%2F&h=e1d3aa60\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181122/1470933/</a>"},{"pid":"df3df3386b7b1bc05a44380267ecf135501adf92","tid":911664,"uid":138625,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"屌你真係馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\